https://www.zoltansbasslounge.com/
https://www.thomasmartin.co.uk/

Hi Guys,

Eddie Gomez has been a huge influence on me ever since i've started to listen to Jazz as a kid. He is one of the all time greats imho. His Swing feel and rhythmic approach has always been very exciting for me to listen to. We have filmed this tutorial to give you a glimpse of this special technique Mr Gomez uses. 

Feel free to discuss the topic in the comments, and mention albums you like with Eddie Gomez on Double Bass.

Have a great day, 
Zoltan
